description: Performs FlowSOM (cluster n=15) and views the results with a heatmap and minimum spanning tree. FlowSOM clusters are also visualized in a heatmap using MEM score. 2D plot with flt-SNE and UMAP. Downsampling filter applied (1%).  For use with FlowJo plugin uploaded data.
name: FlowJo Cluster Explorer #2 - Advanced
